{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/tech/2021/02/03/行列式.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"ed2f109b-a418-509b-a7de-ae739d53cb1f","excerpt":"行列式 二阶行列式计算，对角线相剪,  下三角行列式  上三角行列式  对角线对称  范德蒙行列式  余子式：删掉元素的横纵行得到的行列式  代数余子式： n…","html":"<h1>行列式</h1>\n<p>二阶行列式计算，对角线相剪, <code class=\"language-text\">D = a*b-b*c</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\">| a b |\n| c d |</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>下三角行列式 <code class=\"language-text\">D = a*c*f</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\">| a 0 0 |\n| b c 0 |\n| d e f |</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>上三角行列式 <code class=\"language-text\">D = a*d*f</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\">| a b c |\n| 0 d e |\n| 0 0 f |</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>对角线对称 <code class=\"language-text\">D = ((x-y)^(3-1))*(x + (3-1)*y)</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\">| x y y |\n| y x y |\n| y y x |</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>范德蒙行列式 <code class=\"language-text\">D = (b-a)*(c-a)*(c-b)</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\">| a^0 b^0 c^0 |\n| a^1 b^1 c^1 |\n| a^2 b^2 c^2 |</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>余子式：删掉元素的横纵行得到的行列式 <code class=\"language-text\">M&lt;ij&gt;</code></p>\n<p>代数余子式：<code class=\"language-text\">A&lt;ij&gt; = (-1)^(i+j)\\*M&lt;ij&gt;</code></p>\n<p>n 阶行列式等于某一行或者某一列的代数余子式的和。</p>\n<p>某元素纵向代数余子式和 = 某元素横向代数余子式和。</p>\n<p>行列式转置之后值不变, <code class=\"language-text\">|A&lt;T&gt;| = |A|</code>。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\">| a b c | | a d h |\n| d e f | | b e i |\n| h i j | | c f j |</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>行列式拆解</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\">| a+x b+x c+x |   | a b c |   | x x x |\n| d   e   f   | = | d e f | + | d e f |\n| h   i   j   |   | h i j |   | h i j |</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>某行或者某列加倍并加到另一行值不变。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\">| a b c |   | a+d*k b+e*k c+f*k |\n| d e f | = | d     e     f     |\n| h i j |   | h     i     j     |</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>副对角线行列式 <code class=\"language-text\">D = ((-1)^(3*(3-1)/2))*a*b*d</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\">| 0 0 a |\n| 0 b c |\n| d e f |</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>特殊的拉普拉斯展开式 <code class=\"language-text\">|A|·|B|</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\">| A C |\n| 0 B |</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\">| A 0 |\n| C B |</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>另一个特殊的拉普拉斯展开式<code class=\"language-text\">((-1)^(m*n))|A|·|B|</code></p>\n<p>···\n| 0 A |\n| B C |\n···</p>\n<p>···\n| C A |\n| B 0 |\n···</p>","frontmatter":{"category":"tech"},"fields":{"slug":"/tech/2021/02/03/行列式.html","date":"February 03, 2021","title":"行列式"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/tech/2021/02/03/行列式.html","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/tech/2021/01/25/一个练习打字的网站.html","title":"一个练习打字的网站"},"frontmatter":{"category":"tech"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/plan/2021/02/03/二月计划.html","title":"二月计划"},"frontmatter":{"category":"plan"}}}}}